cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language processing tasks such as part-of-speech tagging and lemmatization. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of bidirectional RNNs suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the mention of character-level embeddings suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as well.
